Privacy Policy

This application is a personal project that connects to Pinterest via OAuth
to analyze a user’s saved Pins and Boards in order to generate a monthly
summary (“Pinterest Wrapped”).

Data Accessed:
- Pinterest account identifier
- Boards and Pins metadata

Data Usage:
- Data is used solely to generate user-facing analytics
- No data is sold or shared with third parties

Data Storage:
- Data may be stored securely to enable monthly summaries
- Users may revoke access at any time through their Pinterest account settings

Contact:
valivetiveda@gmail.com
